# ⚠️ Hard Truth

If you skip ANY of these, you are NOT at exchange-level:

* no HSM → 🔓 keys stealable
* no rotation → 🔓 long-term compromise
* no identity → 🔓 lateral movement
* no enclave → 🔓 memory attack risk

